description:
AccountInfo

Adds a section under your profile to allow for grabbing users' Profile Pictures, Banners in PNG or GIF, and also Statuses with optional dedicated buttons.

Notice:
As of right now this plugin is broken on Discord versions of 149 and higher.
If you are on this version currently, disable or uninstall the plugin until a patch is rolled out.

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/acquitelol/account-info/main/dist/AccountInfo.js
Source: https://github.com/acquitelol/account-info/

 

(Latest: 1.3.7 stable)
